title: Clean Flat GUI Elements
description: 4216 flat vector icons at 3 resolutions and 6732 GUI shapes.
longDescription:
It include 4216 vector icons at 3 resolutions. Also it include 6732 shapes.We provide these GUI elements with high quality png and psd files.

Documnet
technicalDetails:
Features:

- PNG files and layered PSD files;

- Basic icons ("basic_icon" folder);

- Basic shapes("basic_shape" folder);


Basic icons:

- 4216 vector icons at each resolution;

- Resolutions: 128x128, 256x256, 512x512;


Basic shapes:

- 6732 shapes;

- bubbles( 834 elements);

- circles( 540 elements);

- specials( hearts, stars, polygons, labels, lines,total 354 elements);

- rectangles(1092 elements);

- squares(1368 elements);

- tags(972 elements);

- trapeziums(960 elements);

- triangles(576 elements).

Dir:

-Content\CleanFlatGUI\Textures

-Content\CleanFlatGUI\FlatGUI_PNG_PSD.zip
